@node "History" "The history of Dizzer..."

@{FG SHINE}____________________________________________________________________________@{FG TEXT}
¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯
                        The history of Dizzer
@{FG SHINE}____________________________________________________________________________@{FG TEXT}
¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯

      · V1.o (05/03/98)  - First ever release of Dizzer [NEVER RELEASED]

      · V1.1 (07/03/98)  - File requester to pack File_ID.DIZ into
                           Cancel Bug fixed, If you choose cancel on the
                           last version it would archive the whole draw,
                           now the program quits!
 
      · V1.11 (07/03/98) - Bigger and better diz, more letters across
                           allowed. When flicking from the lhaing screen
                           back to the diz editor screen it would go
                           all funny, now fixed.

      · V1.2 (07/03/98)  - Now pack dizes into LZX and txt files.

Back to the @{" Main Menu " link "Main" }...

